channel.title: Oh look - The ground - whats that!?
channel.description:
Well, I Was just exploring cannoing on my skiller when i made a wildy cannoe and i ran down to edgy fast so i wouldnt get killed, When i saw lots of people, Its a quitting party, All of a sudden a dds pops out infront of me, i pick it up think tis my lukey day, when just then a ABBYSAL WHIP just poped out infront of me!!!!
Picture: [img]http://img440.imageshack.us/img440/7025/whipid3.png[/img]
